data.description: Returning back to the island getaway for a lucky 3rd year meant that the Downhill Division had one thing on their mind... win everything! data.title: Star Wars x Santa Cruz Skateboards
data.description:
The Santa Cruz team gets a little help introducing the New Star Wars collection of Decks and Cruzers from an all too familiar villain.

Santa Cruz Skateboards is honored to collaborate with Lucasfilm to present our Exclusive Special Edition Star Wars collection of Decks and Cruzers.

Known for some of the most iconic graphics in skateboarding history, Santa Cruz has created new, exclusive interpretations of your favorite characters.

Featuring Emmanuel Guzman, Justin Strubing, Sid Melvin, Shuriken Shannon, Josh Borden, Jason Jessee and Darth Vader.

Filmed on location in San Francisco CA.

Filmed and edited by Joe Perrin
Additional filming by Carson Lee 

Music: "Trigger" by Buck Buck Buck

data.title: First Wave - Mick Fanning Returns to J'BAY, South Africa
data.description:
Mick Fanning, three-time WSL Champion, has returned to South Africa to contest the J'Bay Open. Fanning became the subject of international headlines during last year’s event where he was attacked on live television by what is believed to be a 12-to-15-foot Great White Shark.

Filmed and edited by Paul Daniel

data.title: Rip Curl Dominates 2016 USA Surfing Championships
data.description:
Rip Curl's top junior surfers left their mark at the prestigious USA Surfing Championship at Lower Trestles, Ca. The team took home 3 Championship Titles, 2 runner-ups, and a 4th place finish. Rip Curl couldn't be more proud of this squad for all their efforts and achievements. Congrats team!

Starring: 
- Diego Ferri | U12 Runner-Up
- Alyssa Spencer | U14 2nd & U16 4th Place
- Robbie Goodwin | U12 Champion
- Brisa Hennessy | U18 Champion
- Crosby Colapinto | U16 Champion

Video/Edit: Justin Jung

data.title: ROXY POP SURF
data.description:
Roxy Pop Surf is an iconic swim collection - marrying fashion-forward design with technology that easily transition from water to sand. Pop Surf features bold bikinis, psychedelic maillots, cropped swim tops, leggy tank dresses, innovative rashguards, quick-dry boar dies and edgy surf leggings. Mix it, match it, and make it your own! Because every surfer has her own unique style on and off the board. 

ATHLETES: 
Stephanie Gilmore
Monyca Oleogram 

LOCATION: 
Waikiki

data.title: Roxy Pro France 2013, September 24th - 30th
data.description:
Following the postponement of the Roxy Pro in Biarritz, the world's top 17 women surfers will, exceptionally, be joining up with their male counterparts for a special meeting of the best surfers on the planet from September 24th! 
 
And so it's a dream line-up expected on the world famous beach breaks of south-west France at the end of the summer... 

We're so excited about this exceptional event coming up that we can't resist to offer you a little taster of what's to come in just a few days time!

LOCATION:
France

ATHLETE: 
Sally Fitzgibbons, Lee-Ann Curren, Stephanie Gilmore, Lisa Andersen, Bianca Buitendag

data.title: The 2013 ROXY Montauk Classic with Stephanie Gilmore in Ditc
data.description:
The Inaugural #ROXYMontaukClassic event was held at Ditch Plains in Montauk, NY. The event brought in locals as well as avid surfers all the way from Florida, Illinois, Hawaii and beyond! Over 100 participants competed for prizes including Paul Mitchell product, local shop Air & Speed gift cards, and tons of Roxy goodies. Five time World Champion, Stephanie Gilmore, World Longboard Champion, Kelia Moniz and Monyca Byrne-Wickey were on site signing autographs, handing out awards and schmoozing and taking pictures with the elated crowd.


ATHLETES: 
5x World Surfing Champion Stephanie Gilmore
2012 ASP World Longboard Champion Kelia Moniz 
Monyca Byrne Wickey 

LOCATION: 
Ditch Plains, Montauk, NY

MUSIC: 
Artist: Steven Milne
Track: Best of Times
